tality by minorities also exacts an emotional toll that is pervasive, yet largely hidden from view. The emotional burden leads to an increase in psychological and physical health consequences, as well as behavioral changes. <span class="read-more-wrap font-3"><a class="read-more" href="https://neurosciencenews.com/racial-disparity-police-brutality-16545/">Read More</a></span></div></div></div></article><article class="tipi-xs-12 elements-location-1 clearfix with-fi ani-base article-ani article-ani-1 shape-s tipi-s-typo stack-1 stack-design-1 separation-border separation-border-style loop-1 preview-classic preview__img-shape-s preview-21 img-ani-base img-ani-1 img-color-hover-base img-color-hover-1 elements-design-1 post-65882 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-featured category-neuroscience tag-blood-vessels tag-brain-research tag-chromatin tag-genetics tag-inflammation tag-max-planck-institute tag-neurobiology tag-neuroscience tag-tlr4"><div class="preview-mini-wrap clearfix"><div class="mask"><a href="https://neurosciencenews.com/brain-blood-vessels-16544/" class="mask-img"><img width="849" height="849" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20849%20849'%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="attachment-zeen-390-390 size-zeen-390-390 wp-post-image" alt="This shows blood vessels" data-lazy-srcset="https://neurosciencenews.com/files/2020/06/neuron-blood-vessel-neuroscienews-849x849.jpg 849w, https://neurosciencenews.com/files/2020/06/neuron-blood-vessel-neuroscienews-100x100.jpg 100w, https://neurosciencenews.com/files/2020/06/neuron-blood-vessel-neuroscienews-293x293.jpg 293w, https://neurosciencenews.com/files/2020/06/neuron-blood-vessel-neuroscienews-752x752.jpg 752w, https://neurosciencenews.com/files/2020/06/neuron-blood-vessel-neuroscienews-1044x1044.jpg 1044w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 849px) 100vw, 849px" data-lazy-src="https://neurosciencenews.com/files/2020/06/neuron-blood-vessel-