More</a></span></div></div></div></article><article class="tipi-xs-12 elements-location-1 clearfix with-fi ani-base article-ani article-ani-1 shape-s tipi-s-typo stack-1 stack-design-1 separation-border separation-border-style loop-2 preview-classic preview__img-shape-s preview-21 img-ani-base img-ani-1 img-color-hover-base img-color-hover-1 elements-design-1 post-65878 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-featured category-neuroscience category-visual-neuroscience tag-brain-research tag-information-processing tag-motion tag-neurobiology tag-neuroscience tag-university-of-rochester tag-visual-neuroscience tag-visual-processing tag-visual-system"><div class="preview-mini-wrap clearfix"><div class="mask"><a href="https://neurosciencenews.com/motion-information-processing-16543/" class="mask-img"><img width="800" height="480" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20800%20480'%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="attachment-zeen-390-390 size-zeen-390-390 wp-post-image" alt="This shows women playing soccer" data-lazy-srcset="https://neurosciencenews.com/files/2020/06/motion-information-processing-neurosicneews.jpg 800w, https://neurosciencenews.com/files/2020/06/motion-information-processing-neurosicneews-300x180.jpg 300w, https://neurosciencenews.com/files/2020/06/motion-information-processing-neurosicneews-752x451.jpg 752w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" data-lazy-src="https://neurosciencenews.com/files/2020/06/motion-information-processing-neurosicneews.jpg" /><noscript><img width="800" height="480" src="https://neurosciencenews.com/files/2020/06/motion-information-processing-neurosicneews.jpg" class="attachment-zeen-390-390 size-zeen-390-390 wp-post-image" alt="This shows women playing soccer" srcset="https://neurosciencenews.com/files/2020/06/motion-information-processing-neurosicneews.jpg 800w, https://neurosciencenews.com/files/2020/06/motion-information-processing-neuros